h2 Composition

p What if multiple sagas have common logic?

p Sagas can be composed to call one another

pre
  code.lang-javascript
    .fragment
      | function* confirm() {
      |   // Basic confirmation flow //
      | }
    |
    .fragment
      | function* save() {
      |   // Another Saga can be executed via 'call'
      |   yield call(confirm);
      | }
    |
    .fragment
      | function* delete() {
      |   // Another Saga can also leverage it
      |  yield call(confirm);
      | }
    |
